  "texts": [
    "Recent research explores LLM-based monitors to evaluate (Bhatt et al., 2023) and moderate (Inan et al., 2023; Zhang et al., 2024) LLMgenerated content.",
    "Equipped with tool usage and interacting with environments, LLM agents unlock novel real-world safety issues, opening up research on behavioral safety (Ruan et al., 2024; Naihin et al., 2023; Tian et al., 2023; Zhan et al., 2024) of LLM agents within diverse environments.",
    "As a pioneer work on agent safety, ToolEmu (Ruan et al., 2024) implemented a GPT-4 powered emulator with diverse tools and scenarios to provide interactive environments for LLM agents and a GPT-4 evaluator to identify risks in agent execution.",
    "Our work furthermore evaluates risk awareness of LLMs to enhance agent safety in diverse scenarios.",
    "Risk awareness is crucial for the safe execution of LLM agents in interactive environments."
  ],
